data.description: PRICE REDUCTION!! Welcome to your dream home! This stunning property boasts immaculate all concrete block construction, offering both durability and modern elegance. With 4 bedrooms, 2 1/2 bathrooms, and a 2-car garage, this smart home has everything you need for comfortable and luxurious living. Step into the master bedroom, where you'll find the perfect retreat with his and hers closets and a spacious en-suite bathroom. Upstairs, the large laundry room is thoughtfully situated near the bedrooms for utmost convenience.The heart of this home is the open concept kitchen, featuring exquisite granite countertops, a generous island, and a walk-in pantry that will delight the chef in you. Embrace sustainable living with the added benefit of Solar Panels and a smart water heater. Your peace of mind is further enhanced by a top-notch security system. Each room is equipped with ceiling fans to ensure your comfort year-round. Plus, enjoy the reassurance of a comprehensive home warranty that covers all your appliances, providing worry-free living. Storage will never be a concern with ample spaces to keep your belongings organized. Discover the inviting community Clubhouse, complete with a well-equipped gym and a resort-style pool – perfect for relaxation and socializing. Explore the community's abundant amenities including miles of picturesque walking trails, tranquil lakes, dedicated bicycle lanes, and a covered playground. Conveniently situated just minutes away from I-75/US HWY 301, shopping centers, and the esteemed St Joseph Hospital, this home also offers the advantage of being close to the brand-new Sumner High School, ensuring an easy and enjoyable daily routine.  Don't miss the chance to make this impeccable property your own. Schedule your showing today and experience the epitome of modern living in a vibrant and welcoming community. Your new lifestyle awaits! Seller will pay up to $5000 in closing costs.
